headline: Allegion is the First Security Solutions Provider to Support Mobile Credentials on Wear OS by Google Smartwatches
summary: Allegion US, a leader in security products and solutions, is the first to support mobile credentials in Google Wallet™ on Wear OS smartwatches. Available starting December 9, 2024, for all Schlage® mobile credentials currently offered in Google Wallet on Android™ such as student IDs and employee badges, the solution equips Wear OS smartwatch users with convenience, enhanced security and seamless access.
